metadata.name: Morning Glory
metadata.description:
Part of a series of black and white photos I took using my iPhone, depicting random moments of my life in Dubai.  

Morning Glory was originally a pink rubber massage ball which I filtered the f*ck out of, so that it ended up resembling a morning star, a weapon used in medieval times.  I called it that because despite being an item used in the treatment of sore muscles, this thing hurts like hell.
